                <h1>Who Owns Salesforce? The Complete Ownership Breakdown</h1>
                <p>Salesforce is owned by Salesforce Inc., a cloud-based software company founded in 1999 by Marc Benioff and Parker Harris. The company specializes in customer relationship management (CRM) and offers a variety of tools and services to help businesses enhance their customer interactions and streamline operations. With a strong market presence, Salesforce ranks among the top players in the tech industry.</p>
